<br>When you feel uninspired and lack creativity, diffusing rosemary may increase alpha brain waves to give you a jumpstart. These are electrical impulses in the brain that keep you mentally coordinated. 
<br>
<br>With a moderate dose of exercise in the mornings and a bottle of rosemary oil nearby, you'll be able to think with clarity. 
